Regarding the geometry of the handle, an improved ergonomic handle shape could include a large palmar grip surface and the combination of precision and turning ability.21 In the same study it is also stated that the handle with the shaft should maintain a \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
