(a) The seven discrete joystick positions on the same 3D-printed rotating joystick-body handle prototype. The axis of rotation of the joystick-body and the angle of each position highlight the rotating function. (b) The hand at its resting position, (c) (left to right and top to bottom) The handle held by a small left hand, a small right hand, a large left hand, and a large right hand, and (d) Thumb adduction (left), thumb abduction (right).

